TopicTitle: Last person to post is winner

Articles.Content:
Welp, I am at loss for words. Except for these:

I am winning.

Also, here is a picture I drew and posted in the fan art forum:

The rocket waiting to launch is made of NovaPunch parts, as is the wreckage at the bottom. The black figures are kerbals in silhouette. At the top there is a tiny Probodobodyne satellite. The water tower can be seen at the right, with a sniper kerbal on it, whom just finished shooting down the rocket to the left exploding. Two SRBs impacted just below the explosion, next to the guy who is parachuting. Two palm trees from 8.5 are on fire, next to .14\'s tracking station. At the upper-bottom right corner is a teacher kerbal showing the students a launch. Just below him a kerbal is drinking radioactive liquid from a BACE nuclear reactor. In between the water tower and the rocket launch there is a UFO from a mod pack I cannot remember. A Mei Long capsule is retroburning at the very top with its parachute deployed. To the right of the explosion (large) there is a regular pod losing its parachute, and just above it is a spaceplane breaking during reentry. An ICBM is launching, and a few kerbals are surrendering atop the launch tower.
